WEBVTT

00:09:29.434 --> 00:09:30.747
What you see in the picture

00:09:30.771 --> 00:09:33.631
is the beginning of 426
primary school children

00:09:33.655 --> 00:09:36.400
who were walked up the hill
by the head teacher,

00:09:36.424 --> 00:09:39.227
who didn't want them
to lose this opportunity.

00:09:39.251 --> 00:09:41.661
And just as happens in the Nevada desert,

00:09:41.685 --> 00:09:44.154
though in slightly different temperatures,

00:09:44.178 --> 00:09:47.891
the people of this community,
65,000 of them,

00:09:47.915 --> 00:09:53.272
turned out to write their grief,
their pain, their hope,

00:09:53.296 --> 00:09:55.083
their hopes for the future,

00:09:55.107 --> 00:09:56.295
their love.

00:09:56.319 --> 00:09:58.452
Because in the end,
this is only about love.

00:09:59.032 --> 00:10:01.605
They live in a post-conflict society: